graph.original_query: Create a dark-themed, modern multi-page landing website using Flowbite + Tailwind CSS via CDN (no build tools), with 4 pages: index.html (hero with fullscreen background image from picsum.photos or placeholder.com, features, testimonials, CTA, footer with social icons), about.html (mission statement, timeline or values, team cards), products.html (6â€“8 product/service cards in a grid with title, description, image, price, optional filters), and contact.html (contact form with name/email/message, map placeholder or location card, support links), using consistent dark mode theme, responsive layout, shared header/footer, no lorem ipsum, proper meta tags and titles, and only HTML/CSS/JS. Call CoderAgent atleast 9-10 times for different exhaustive but specific tasks as this is a detailed project. Remember CoderAgent is stateless and can't see other outputs. So you will have to be very specific in creating only parts else it will create full htmls. Make sure that files are properly integrated at the end.
